headline: Kroger Announces First Quarter Conference Call with Investors
summary: The Kroger Co. (NYSE: KR) announced today it will host its first quarter 2025 earnings conference call at 10:00 a.m. ET on Friday, June 20, 2025. Kroger's management team will comment on financial and operational results for the first quarter 2025.
